OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPlenty of sunshine, though low
OL,6,Fcloud affecting some North Sea coasts.
OL,7,FHot for most, exceptionally so across
OL,8,Fsouthern and central parts of England
OL,9,Fand Wales. Breezier than Wednesday.
OL,10,FWetter and cloudier for northwest
OL,11,FScotland, with spells of heavy rain.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain in the northwest turning
OL,14,Fthundery. Further thunderstorms with
OL,15,Fstrong gusty winds developing across
OL,16,Fsouthwest England during Thursday
OL,17,Fevening before spreading
OL,18,Fnortheastwards overnight. Warm and
OL,19,Fhumid for all.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
