OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FRather cloudy across northern
OL,6,Fregions with outbreaks of rain and
OL,7,Fthunderstorms, accompanied by hail and
OL,8,Fgusty winds. Peak heat transferring to
OL,9,Feastern England, with temperatures
OL,10,Ffurther west dropping slightly.
